| `F_SL(rho)` | `remains ambiguous` | the family only gives `t_next = 1 - O(rho)` or `> 1`, so the exact terminal witness demanded by the frozen late clause is not fixed uniformly |

### Verdict

- `[INFERRED]` Overall status:
  `discarded`.
