+### Survivor 1 - Repaired `Template-Defect Near-Closure`
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Exact criterion:
+
+  ```text
+  Fix the role hierarchy
+  (h_seed, h_clk, h_amp, h_rot, h_next) = (1/16, 1/4, 1, 2, 2)
+  and eps_ref = 1/64.
+
+  Let F_h(A,B,C,D,E)
+    := (
+         -h_rot C D - h_clk A B - h_seed A C,
+          h_clk A^2 - h_amp C^2,
+          h_seed A^2 + h_amp B C,
+          h_rot C A - h_next D E,
+          h_next D^2
+       ).
+
+  Let
+  ||X||_role
+    := max(
+         |X_A|,
+         h_clk^(-1) |X_B|,
+         h_seed^(-1) |X_C|,
+         h_rot^(-1) |X_D|,
+         h_next^(-1) |X_E|
+       ).
+
+  Define
+  Delta_tmpl(P_n; I)
+    := sup_{t in I}
+       || Pi_{P_n} N(u,u)(t) - F_h(U_{P_n}(t)) ||_role
+       /
+       ( || F_h(U_{P_n}(t)) ||_role + eps_ref ),
+
+  Delta_spec(P_n; I)
+    := sup_{t in I}
+       || Pi_{S_n} N(u,u)(t) ||_role
+       /
+       ( || F_h(U_{P_n}(t)) ||_role + eps_ref ).
+  ```
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Repaired thresholds:
+
+  ```text
+  Delta_tmpl <= lambda_tmpl = 1/4
+  Delta_spec <= lambda_spec = 49/256.
+  ```
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Packet semantics:
+  same shared frozen ledger above; no change to packet class, channel list,
+  spectator partition, sign sheet, or window.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Carried-friendly witness:
+  `F_SL(1/16)`,
+  because it is the worst recorded friendly packet on both repaired defect
+  coordinates.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Hostile comparator:
+  `F_DT(delta, eta)`,
+  which remains a hostile failure on this gate by late rotor / next-shell
+  collapse on the same frozen ledger.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Invariant downstream gate:
+
+  ```text
+  G_tmpl(P_n; I) = (Delta_tmpl, Delta_spec).
+  ```
+
+- `[INFERRED]` Step-6 status:
+  promote unchanged.
